<Link id="l00009" /><CodeLine lineNumber="9"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// This file defines the ValueMap class.  ValueMap maps Value&#42; or any subclass</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00010" /><CodeLine lineNumber="10"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// to an arbitrary other type.  It provides the DenseMap interface but updates</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00011" /><CodeLine lineNumber="11"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// itself to remain safe when keys are RAUWed or deleted.  By default, when a</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00012" /><CodeLine lineNumber="12"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// key is RAUWed from V1 to V2, the old mapping V1-&gt;target is removed, and a new</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00013" /><CodeLine lineNumber="13"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// mapping V2-&gt;target is added.  If V2 already existed, its old target is</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00014" /><CodeLine lineNumber="14"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// overwritten.  When a key is deleted, its mapping is removed.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00015" /><CodeLine lineNumber="15"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00016" /><CodeLine lineNumber="16"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// You can override a ValueMap&#39;s Config parameter to control exactly what</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00017" /><CodeLine lineNumber="17"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// happens on RAUW and destruction and to get called back on each event.  It&#39;s</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00018" /><CodeLine lineNumber="18"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// legal to call back into the ValueMap from a Config&#39;s callbacks.  Config</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00019" /><CodeLine lineNumber="19"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// parameters should inherit from ValueMapConfig&lt;KeyT&gt; to get default</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00020" /><CodeLine lineNumber="20"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// implementations of all the methods ValueMap uses.  See ValueMapConfig for</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00021" /><CodeLine lineNumber="21"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// documentation of the functions you can override.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00022" /><CodeLine lineNumber="22"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00023" /><CodeLine lineNumber="23"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//===----------------------------------------------------------------------===//</span></CodeLine>
